華南海鮮市場疫情源自進口海產品？專家：不排除冷鏈傳入可能，但缺乏足夠證據支撐（環球時報）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thenewslens.com/article/143484\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F143484&d=VbAd486K8RrC2DEUtq3b5ugMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=3ed0ea29\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thenewslens.com/article/143484</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T13:29:02.000Z","msg":"唔進口，剩食草，樹皮都夠食十年，仲有幾十億蝗蟲存糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6cbd95a8ec703992c0e7ffa11c560fff6e97319","tid":2291002,"uid":8410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T13:30:43.000Z","msg":"要進口就要課金去做支那廢test <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6852fd915fa66d9591f5a940308c51cdd75ca33","tid":2291002,"uid":327169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T13:38:16.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支那人表示，有病菌都乾淨過支那製造!</span>"},{"pid":"b8a9f68d3dcd6cb92ccff467b5aff887da9962bc","tid":2291002,"uid":35087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T13:39:25.000Z","msg":"唔好賣啦"},{"pid":"72c762ee230a82ecc933c9a7b4f06452f357ccbe","tid":2291002,"uid":51583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T13:40:10.000Z","msg":"等睇全世界一齊玩番佢"},{"pid":"b33d348e3efea8f7b05cec84992819f6a83f378b","tid":2291002,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T13:41:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dr